This is an open-label phase 1A/1B study to assess the safety, tolerability and pharmacokinetics of SBP-101 when combined with nab-paclitaxel and gemcitabine in subjects with previously untreated metastatic pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma and to identify a recommended phase 2 dose.

 The study will also assess preliminary efficacy of the 3-drug treatment combination.

